    <div class="jumbotron">
      <h1 class="display-4">Hello, there!</h1>
      <p class="lead">This is a website called TinyApp. We love to make things smaller for you! Looking for fit a
        character limit in your favourite social media application? Throw your URL into our engine and BAM! We'll give
        you back a unique six digit link that you can use from now until eternity!</p>
      <hr class="my-4">
      <p>To store the tiny links that you make here in TinyApp, just register for an account and we'll keep them safe
        for the next time
        you visit!</p>
      <p class="lead">
        <a class="btn btn-info btn-lg" href="/register" role="button">Register Now!</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
